task.summary: Got followage working and added help command
Added a !serverage command to allow people to set the start date of their server and the bot will tell people when the server started and how many days it has been live for.
Added a !youtube command which will lookup the current channel's youtube channel and tell the sender their last uploads title, days since it was uploaded, and give them the url.
Working on getting rid of kraken api completely

Completely removed the kraken api, and added an auto clear function that is configurable. it will auto clear chat every x amount of minutes specified in the config(!autoClear minutes will set that number also).
Updating the !clips command to allow mods and streamer to save their favorite clips.
Finished (some what) implementing the saving and getting of favorite clips.
Implemented pals, this will allow the stream to add pals then it will check if their pal is live and playing the same game if so it will spit out a multi-twitch stream link.
Moved variables to more suitable classes, changed the loadFollows function to save list of followers to channel file and isFollowing now checks the file instead.
Moved variables to more suitable classes, changed the loadFollows function to save list of followers to channel file and isFollowing now checks the file instead.
Added a point and dueling system. Points are given every minute(as of now) to followers of the channel.
